## Requirements

```
Python        >= 3.8
pandas        >= 1.0
numpy         >= 1.19
scikit-learn  >= 0.24
imbalanced-learn >= 0.8
matplotlib
seaborn
```

Install all at once:
```bash
pip install pandas numpy scikit-learn imbalanced-learn matplotlib seaborn
```

Optional (adds XGBoost to model comparison):
```bash
pip install xgboost
```
